    public class SelectUsersPopupWindow
extends PopupWindow
    A popup window that is used to select people. Two possible modes: - multiselect: displays two tables that allow to select users from the left table to the table on the right - non-multiselect: one table where only one user can be chosen from. SubmitEventListener can be attached to listen to completion of the selection. The selected user(s) can be retrieved using getSelectedUserId() ,getSelectedUserIds() and getSelectedUserRole(String).
    作者:
    Joram Barrez
